OL,3,CIsland's doctors claim health service
OL,4,Cis 'poor place to work'
OL,6,FDoctors on the Isle of Man are
OL,7,Fdisillusioned with their jobs - with a
OL,8,Flack of confidence in management and a
OL,9,Fpoor culture to blame.
OL,11,FA survey by the British Medical
OL,12,FAssociation found only 15% of those
OL,13,Fwho took part would recommend the
OL,14,FIsland's main healthcare provider Manx
OL,15,FCare, as a good place to work.
OL,17,FOf those who responded, only 9% felt
OL,18,Fthey were being heard , while 81%
OL,19,Fdisagreed with the statement 'Manx
OL,20,FCare has a positive culture'.
