OL,3,CIsland's doctors claim health service
OL,4,Cis 'poor place to work'
OL,6,FThe service, which launched in 2021,
OL,7,Fsays it is working with doctors to
OL,8,Fresolve their differences.
OL,10,FDr Prakash Thiagarajan, the Chair of
OL,11,Fthe Isle of Man Medical Society said
OL,12,Fmany felt undervalued.
OL,14,F"Most of the doctors feel they have
OL,15,Fthings done to them rather than being
OL,16,Fpart of the decision making, and they
OL,17,Fdon't feel like they're valued
OL,18,Fenough," he said.
