OL,3,CIsland's doctors claim health service
OL,4,Cis 'poor place to work'
OL,6,F"They feel undervalued and over-
OL,7,Fstretched without sufficient resource
OL,8,Fto help them."
OL,10,FDr Prakash Thiagarajan says doctors
OL,11,Ffeel undervalued
OL,13,FMany of the problems, it is claimed,
OL,14,Fstem from the main hospital on the
OL,15,FIsland, Noble's Hospital.
OL,17,FThe 'Culture of Care Barometer'
OL,18,Fcollected 82 responses, after being
OL,19,Fsent to all 155 doctors working
OL,20,Fdirectly for Manx Care.
