OL,6,F77% of respondents to the survey
OL,7,Fdisagreed that Manx Care managers know
OL,8,Fhow things really are, and only 9%
OL,9,Fbelieve that the trust listens to
OL,10,Fstaff views.
OL,12,FMore than half also strongly disagree
OL,13,Fthat Manx Care values the service
OL,14,Fdoctors provide.
