OL,3,CIsland's doctors claim health service
OL,4,Cis 'poor place to work'
OL,6,FChair of council of the BMA, Professor
OL,7,FPhil Banfield said: "I've heard
OL,8,Frepeatedly over the last two years
OL,9,Ffrom doctors on the Isle of Man just
OL,10,Fhow deeply frustrated they are at
OL,11,Fwork, so these results are no surprise
OL,12,Fto me.
OL,14,F"The culture that doctors work in is
OL,15,Fintrinsically tied to the quality of
OL,16,Fcare they are able to give, so these
OL,17,Fresults should concern us all.
