OL,3,CIsland's doctors claim health service
OL,4,Cis 'poor place to work'
OL,6,F"We hope to be proven wrong, for the
OL,7,Fsake of doctors who deserve better
OL,8,Fworking lives than this ` and for
OL,9,Fpatients on the Isle of Man who must
OL,10,Freceive the best care possible."
OL,12,FManx Care say it is "disappointed with
OL,13,Fthe results", adding it may not agree
OL,14,Fwith what the doctors are saying, but
OL,15,Fit is "willing to listen".
OL,17,FTeresa Cope, CEO of Manx Care, said:
OL,18,F"I do want to get into the detail and
OL,19,Fhave the discussion with colleagues as
OL,20,Fto actually who do they feel is not
OL,21,Flistening.
