OL,3,CIsland's doctors claim health service
OL,4,Cis 'poor place to work'
OL,6,F"That's the bit we need to get
OL,7,Funderneath, where is that disconnect
OL,8,Fhappening and how do we resolve it."
OL,10,FShe added: "We've got to get this into
OL,11,Fperspective, I meet clinicians every
OL,12,Fday, formally and informally, and on
OL,13,Fthe corridors, many of them are very
OL,14,Fproud to work at Manx Care.
OL,16,FIn a statement after the survey
OL,17,Fresults, it said the organisation has
OL,18,F"successfully attracted permanent
OL,19,Fmedical staff" over the past couple of
OL,20,Fyears, during a 'financially
OL,21,Fchallenging' time.
