OL,3,CIsland's doctors claim health service
OL,4,Cis 'poor place to work'
OL,6,FThis includes restricting money
OL,7,Favailable to negotiate pay settlements
OL,8,Ffor doctors, which remains unresolved.
OL,10,FAfter discussions with the BMA, the
OL,11,FManx Care Board agreed to pay 6% for
OL,12,Fthe last year, but acknowledged it
OL,13,Fdoes not end the pay dispute.
OL,15,FAn all-staff survey is now being
OL,16,Fcirculated to get a broader view of
OL,17,Fany issues, as doctors decide their
OL,18,Fnext move.
